36.Bh5 $1 { Gukesh relentlessly goes forwards. The Black king has no squares so Gukesh looks for checkmating possibilities. } ( 36.Qg4 { is also strong here. } ) Qxe4  ( 36...Ng7 37.Bxg7+ { Black now has the choice of giving up the queen or soon getting mated after } 37...Kg8 38.Bxf6+ ) ( 36...Rc7 37.Bxe8 { White is winning. Recapturing the bishop leads to mate in 2. } ) 
