41.Rxe4  {[%cal Be4e7]} {[%csl Be7]} {[%cal Be7a7]} {[%csl Ba7]} { With accurate calculation Gukesh knows this move is possible. White's rook can get behind the pawn to stop it. This is the only move that wins for White. } ( 41.Ra1 Nb4 42.Kc3 Nxd5+= ) a2  
