38.Rb6  Rb2  
39.g5  { Black resigned, he will not be able to defend on both sides of the board. Kalle Kiik born 1963 became an International Master in 1993. This game was played in round two of the 2022 Olympiad. India 2 beat Estonia 4-0. }  1-0


