36.g4  ( { At the press conference immediately after the game, Gukesh said 'I wanted to show you one cute line...' } 36.Ncxd6 Rf4+ 37.Kg5 Qg3+ 38.Nxg3 Nh7+ 39.Kxh5 g6+ 40.Kh6 Rh4+ 41.Nh5 Rxh5# ) ( { Gukesh also spoke with Sagar Shah and Amruta and showed further variations: } 36.Ncxd6 Rf4+ 37.g4 Rxg4# ) ( { And } 36.Ncxd6 Rf4+ 37.Kg5 Rg4+ 38.hxg4 Nh7# { He had seen it all during the game! } ) Rxf5  
