39.Kxh5  Qxh3  {[%cal Bh3h5]} {[%cal Bh7g5]} {[%csl Rh5]} { This game was played in round 8 of the 2024 Candidates. Vidit finished sixth with 6/14, Gukesh won with 9/14. }  0-1


