{ White's capture 25. [Nxc7] has landed us in a fiendishly complex position. Can you calculate your way to victory as Black from here? } Qxc7  { The only good move for Black. Gukesh takes the offered piece. While navigating the forks and pins over the next few moves he ensures he keeps his major pieces active. } 
