33.Bd6  ( { Black also wins after } 33.Qxa2 Qxd4 ) Qa5  {[%cal Ba5d5]} {[%cal Ba5e1]} { White resigned here as he cannot avoid a trade of queens, leaving Black a rook up. Although Wei Yi lost this game in the Tata Steel Masters, he managed to defeat Gukesh in the play-off to win the tournament. } ( { Also winning was } 33...Rd2 )  0-1


